      "content": "# User Profile Retrieval Endpoint: GET /user\n\n## Overview\nThis endpoint allows authenticated clients to retrieve comprehensive profile information for the currently logged-in user. It is essential for client-side initialization and verifying user context across the application.\n\n### Request Details\nThis is a simple GET request requiring a valid authentication token in the `Authorization` header.\n\n### Response Body\nThe successful response returns a JSON object containing the user's core details, including `id`, `email`, and `name`.\n\n## Error Handling\nIf authentication fails or the user resource cannot be found, appropriate HTTP status codes will be returned.",
